"1244-00000555-01Z" is silkscreened on the board.
The power adapter included with the device is presumably (it's shown in the FCC photos..) a '''DVE''' DSA-12R-12 AUS 120120 (100-120V ~ 50/60 Hz, 0.3A -> 12VDC, 1A).
